      "para_id": "Q009692.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) The personal god of En-metena , ruler of Lagaš , child of En-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , the builder of Nanše’s lofty temple terrace , is Šul-MUŠxPA ."
    }
